properties.text:
In this example, you can enter a train and travel around the station. To start the train travel, enter it and press [color=#ffff00]\[Space][/color].

Controls:
- [color=#ffff00]\[WASD]:[/color] moves
- [color=#ffff00]\[Space]:[/color] activates the train
- [color=#ffff00]\[Mouse]:[/color] looks around

Press [color=#ffff00]\[Space][/color] to start...
